                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-80-victim581 t18280911-80-viclabel413"></join>. On the 21st of August, about ten o'clock in the morning, the prisoner came into the shop and asked for an ear-ring; I told him I knew nothing about it - while he was talking another one came in and asked to look at a set of castors; while I was getting them the prisoner caught up this candlestick and snuffers and ran out of the shop; he was pursued and taken - he had been to the shop once before making excuses but bought nothing.</p>
               <p>
            
